# TireMaster CSV Sample Analysis Workspace

This directory is prepared for collaborative analysis of TireMaster CSV invoice format.

## Purpose
- Analyze actual TireMaster CSV files to understand structure and format
- Create column mapping configuration
- Identify data transformation requirements
- Test CSV parsing and validation

## Expected Files
- Sample CSV files from TireMaster system
- Format analysis documentation
- Column mapping configuration files
- Test data for validation

## Next Steps
1. Upload representative TireMaster CSV sample files
2. Analyze column structure and data formats
3. Create mapping configuration
4. Test data transformation logic

## Notes
- This workspace is for collaborative work between developer and user
- Files placed here will be used to configure the CSV import system
- All sensitive customer data should be anonymized for testing
